c: 24
v: 55
t: "UAllâh Ubathembisile abo bakholwayo phakathi kwenu, benza nezenzo ezilungileyo okokuba Yena ngokwenene Uza kubanika ukungena esikhundleni (ngolawulo) emhlabeni njengoko wabanikayo abo bangaphambili kubo. Kwanokuba ngenene Uza kubamisela inkolo yabo Ayikhethele bona yaye ngokwenene Uza kubafakela ukhuseleko emva koloyiko lwabo ngenxa yokuba bona banqula Mna, abayamanisi mahlulelane kuM. Kodwa lowo ungakholwayo emva koko abo ngabadeleli abangenantobeko bokwenene"